As we discussed, search engines crawl websites by following links when you link from one place to another

6
00:00:24,870 --> 00:00:25,350
post.

7
00:00:25,590 --> 00:00:28,830
That's a way of signaling that those pages are related.

8
00:00:29,250 --> 00:00:34,740
When it comes to internal linking, you should prioritize the content that you consider to be most important.

9
