28
00:01:53,520 --> 00:01:58,140
So these days, the main thing to think about is whether the anchor text looks natural in your copy

29
00:01:58,140 --> 00:02:00,990
and provides an actual benefit to the end user.

30
00:02:01,230 --> 00:02:07,260
It's OK to use keywords, but don't go overboard and use the same anchor text every time you link to

